title: Heavenly God Mnemonic
summary: A drop of blood from the demon god, destroyed ten thousand mountains and rivers. A roll of scripture, obliterated the cycle of the sun and moon. A collection of mnemonics, bury all the most highs. Yang Qing Xuan received his fated inheritance, and practiced the way of invincibility, and allowed him to run through innumerable geniuses, and open up an everlasting path of becoming the strongest! “I have always win people over by virtue, and those that didn’t are all dead!”
